what you bring up

00:17:49.250 --> 00:17:53.540
which is trying to predict
truly before you actually

00:17:53.540 --> 00:17:58.070
do the experiment, the virtual
searching for materials

00:17:58.070 --> 00:18:00.650
is playing a more and
more important role.

