00:18:15.980 --> 00:18:18.090
the experiment.

00:18:18.090 --> 00:18:22.760
And here's one, this
is from Alfie's group,

00:18:22.760 --> 00:18:24.140
which is, I think,
Cambridge or--

00:18:24.140 --> 00:18:24.848
AUDIENCE: London.

