01:09:41.293 --> 01:09:43.200
See, the problem
is you don't know.

01:09:43.200 --> 01:09:45.220
This is in the end the
fundamental problem.

01:09:45.220 --> 01:09:47.220
It depends on where you fit it.

01:09:47.220 --> 01:09:50.850
If you fit from 11 to 12--

01:09:50.850 --> 01:09:55.850
if you fit from 11 to 12,
then this is your slope.

01:09:55.850 --> 01:09:58.370
Then, you're going
to have this curve.

01:09:58.370 --> 01:10:02.260
If you fit from 1 to 2, you're
going to have this curve.

01:10:04.820 --> 01:10:09.110
And do you see that they
